  "baseRefName": "main",
  "body": "## Summary\n\nAdds the **Strategic Moat & Enterprise Readiness OS (V9)** on top of V1–V8,\nexpanding the repo into an enterprise-ready company operating system with a\ntrust center, demo/sandbox, customer lifecycle, founder delegation, agent\ngovernance, cost control, data room, procurement, QMS, documentation\ngovernance, master index, and deployment verification.\n\n> Branch note: developed and pushed on the session's configured branch\n> `claude/dealix-v9-strategic-enterprise-XVDuc` (per environment policy), not a\n> separately named `final/...` branch.\n\n## Includes\n\n- **13 operating systems** (+ Master Index) as bilingual AR/EN docs under `docs/`:\n  Strategic Moat, Enterprise Readiness, Trust Center, Demo & Sandbox, Customer\n  Lifecycle, Founder Delegation, Agent Governance, Cost Control, Data Room,\n  Procurement, QMS, Documentation Governance, Deployment Verification.\n- **Configs:** `config/demo_scenarios.json`, `config/customer_lifecycle_stages.json`,\n  `config/agent_registry.json`, `config/agent_prompt_library.json`,\n  `config/model_routing_policy.json`, `config/token_budgets.json`,\n  `config/qms_checklists.json`, `data/demo_companies.example.jsonl`.\n- **Demo pack generator:** `scripts/demo_pack_generate.py` (sandbox/sample data only).\n- **14 verify scripts** + **5 aggregate roll-ups** + a master roll-up\n  (`scripts/v9_master_verification.py`), writing JSON to `outputs/v9_verification/`.\n- **14 pytest files** (`tests/test_*_verify.py`, `tests/test_demo_pack_generate.py`).\n- **2 GitHub Actions** (`v9-master-verification.yml`, `v9-enterprise-readiness.yml`):\n  `workflow_dispatch` + `schedule`, `permissions: contents: read`, artifact-only.\n- **Public web pages:** `/trust`, `/security`, `/privacy` under `apps/web/app`.\n- **Reports** for every system plus aggregate control-tower / utilization /\n  command-center reports, and `docs/V9_EVIDENCE_PACK.md`.\n\n## Safety\n\n- No external sending. No SMTP. No WhatsApp/LinkedIn/email outbound. No platform\n  automation. No scraping. No website auto-submit. No live paid-ads launch.\n- No secrets / API keys. No fake traction. No guaranteed ROI. No unverified\n  certifications (status disclosed honestly, templates marked pending review).\n- GitHub Actions are artifact-only and never send externally.\n- **Founder approval remains required** before anything leaves the building.\n\n## Tests Run (local, 2026-06-04)\n\n- `python scripts/v9_master_verification.py` → **V9_MASTER_VERDICT=PASS** (18/18).\n- `pytest` on the 14 V9 test files → **30 passed**.\n- `make env-check` → **OK**.\n- `make security-smoke` → **pre-existing failures** in existing repo files\n  (e.g. `tests/test_billing_moyasar_safety.py`, `docs/ops/GO_LIVE_CHECKLIST_AR.md`);\n  **no V9 file is flagged**. Not introduced by this PR.\n- `make api-contract-check` / `make prod-verify` / `make test` → could not run to\n  completion in this ephemeral environment (missing app runtime deps such as\n  `jose` / DB). Unrelated to V9; the V9 layer is self-contained and its own\n  verifiers and tests pass.\n\n## Final Go/No-Go\n\n**GO:** enterprise readiness preparation · demo pack generation · trust center\ncontent · data room preparation · procurement packet preparation · QMS readiness\n· deployment verification · founder delegation planning.\n\n**NO-GO:** external sending · platform automation · fake certifications · fake\ntraction · unreviewed legal claims · live paid ads.\n\nhttps://claude.ai/code/session_019s42LujQ5QstcTEgmigffk\n\n---\n_Generated by [Claude Code](https://claude.ai/code/session_019s42LujQ5QstcTEgmigffk)_",
