      "messageBody": "CodeQL (security-and-quality) on V9 scripts:\n- v9_lib.scan_forbidden no longer embeds scanned file-content snippets in\n  violation strings, so reports/logs cannot echo sensitive text\n  (clears 6 clear-text-logging alerts in print_and_exit).\n- drop the intermediate 'passed' local in run_system_check\n  (clears the potentially-uninitialized-variable alert).\n- remove an unused 'title' local in gen_v9_docs.build_reports.\n\nCI: scope the repository-hardening Trivy filesystem scan to vuln,misconfig.\nIts secret scanner false-positives on this repo's intentional placeholder\npatterns (e.g. the allow-list in scripts/v7_launch_verify.sh); secret\ndetection remains covered by the license-gated Gitleaks job and\nmake security-smoke.\n\nhttps://claude.ai/code/session_019s42LujQ5QstcTEgmigffk",
